OLER は、IDG OIL の TEMPERATURE を減少させるために ENGINE FAN AIR を使用する。 GENERATOR DRIVE-AIR/OIL COOLER 737-800 24-10 0510 D2-08,\"ACCESS,AIR,AIR/OIL,CASE,COMPONENT,COOLER,COWL,D2-08,DAMAGE,DESCRIPTION,DRIVE,DRIVE-AIR/OIL,ENGINE,FAN,GENERAL,GENERATOR,IDG,INSIDE,INTERNAL,LEFT,LOCATION,LOWER,OIL,OPEN,POSITION,PURPOSE,REVERSER,SECTION,TEMPERATURE,THRUST\",F2-08,pg_24_f2_08,,2026-06-09T10:43:19.548165+00:00,2026-06-09T10:43:19.548165+00:00\r\npg_24_f2_08,24,src_sg_24_ref,24_REF.pdf,66,F2-08,figure,24-10,Generator Drive,GENERATOR DRIVE - AIR/OIL COOLER,GENERATOR DRIVE - AIR/OIL COOLER 737-800 24-10 0510 F2-08 RELOOC LIO/RIA - EVIRD ROTARENEG RELOOC LIO/RIA ESAC NAF ENIGNE )NOITISOP 03:6( DWF,GENERATOR DRIVE - AIR/OIL COOLER 737-800 24-10 0510 F2-08 RELOOC LIO/RIA - EVIRD ROTARENEG RELOOC LIO/RIA ESAC NAF ENIGNE )NOITISOP 03:6( DWF,\"AIR/OIL,COOLER,DRIVE,DWF,ENIGNE,ESAC,EVIRD,F2-08,GENERATOR,LIO/RIA,NAF,NOITISOP,RELOOC,ROTARENEG\",D2-08,pg_24_d2_08,,2026-06-09T10:43:19.548165+00:00,2026-06-09T10:43:19.548165+00:00\r\npg_24_d2_09,24,src_sg_24_ref,24_REF.pdf,67,D2-09,text,24-10,Generator Drive,GENERATOR DRIVE-FUNCTIONAL DESCRIPTION,\"GENERATOR DRIVE-FUNCTIONAL DESCRIPTION 737-800 24-10 0903 D2-09 7. GENERATOR DRIVE -FUNCTIONAL DESCRIPTION A. IDG Functional Description IDGÍAHydromechanical Constant Speed Drive(CSD)SectionyÑOil Cooled Brushless AC GeneratorÅ\\¬³êÄ¢éB IDGÍA³çÉControlyÑExcitation PowerÌ½ßÉPermanent Magnet Generator(PMG)ðà µÄ¢éBCSDÆGenerator ComponentÌ Lubrication yÑCoolingÍA¯¶Oil CircuitÉæèsíêéB CSD SectionÍA24,000 RPMÌConstant SpeedÅGeneratorðñ·B GeneratorÍA115/200v ACA400 Hzð·éB GeneratorÍA90 KVAÌRatingðÁÄ¢éB AC GeneratorÍA3 Phase Brushless MachineÅ éB GeneratorÍAAC Exciter GeneratorÆMain Generator©ç¬éB Permanent Magnet Generator(PMG)ÍAPermanent Magnet RotoryÑPMG Stator©çÈéBGeneratorªñ]·éÆAPMG RotorÍAPMG StatorÉAC VoltageðNd·éBPMG VoltageÍAGenerator Co